    <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

    <section class="header">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dmdbza74n/image/upload/v1693147935/achievementroadmaps/othercideHQ_cigusd.png"
            alt="Othercide Cover" />
    </section>
    <section class="mainSection">
        <div class="middleColumnParent">
            <div class="leftColumn">
                <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dmdbza74n/image/upload/v1693154839/achievementroadmaps/othercideL_bwp4yn.webp"
                    alt="" />
            </div>
            <div class="middleColumnPages">
                <ul class="entryTitles">
                    <li>
                        Time to 100%:<span class="editableTitles">50 hours</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Minimum Playthroughs:<span class="editableTitles">Multiple</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Extra Content required:<span class="editableTitles">0</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Total Achievements:<span class="editableTitles">26</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Single Player:<span class="editableTitles">26</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Multiplayer/CoOp:<span class="editableTitles">0</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Does difficulty affect achievements?:<span class="editableTitles">No</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Do achievements stack?:<span class="editableTitles">No</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Missable:<span class="editableTitles">2 - <span class="achievement">
                                <%= achievements[6].displayName %>
                                <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[6].icon %> alt="" />
                                    <span class="tooltip-text">
                                        <%= achievements[6].description %>
                                    </span>
                                </span>
                            </span>, <span class="achievement">
                                <%= achievements[5].displayName %>
                                <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[5].icon %> alt="" />
                                    <span class="tooltip-text">
                                        <%= achievements[5].description %>
                                    </span>
                                </span>
                            </span></span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Glitched:<span class="editableTitles">0</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Grind:<span class="editableTitles">0</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <div class="aboutGameSection">
                    <h1>Does it worth your time?</h1>
                    <p class="indent">
                        A unique tactical turn-based game. Truly challenging, that requires planning in and out of
                        combat. An easier difficulty option has been added, that can save you some playtime. Although, I
                        find that the original experience the developers aimed for works well, as long as you have the
                        patience. It is a little slow and it can get repetitive, but if you are looking for a challenge
                        it
                        is worth your time.
                    </p>
                    <p class="indent">
                        The game may be challenging, but the achievements are not. You are left to focus on the
                        mechanics
                        and enjoy the game without having to pay any attention on them. Almost all achievements will
                        unlock
                        naturally.
                    </p>
                    <h2>First Playthrough</h2>
                    <p class="indent">
                        The first playthrough will take 95% of the total playtime. You will also unlock 90% of the
                        achievements by the time you defeat the final boss. Story related achievements are:
                        <span class="achievement">
                            <%= achievements[0].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[0].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[0].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>,
                        <span class="achievement">
                            <%= achievements[1].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[1].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[1].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>,
                        <span class="achievement">
                            <%= achievements[2].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[2].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[2].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>,
                        <span class="achievement">
                            <%= achievements[3].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[3].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[3].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>,
                        <span class="achievement">
                            <%= achievements[4].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[4].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[4].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span> and
                        <span class="achievement">
                            <%= achievements[7].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[7].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[7].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>. For restarting the campaign you will unlock
                        <span class="achievement">
                            <%= achievements[11].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[11].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[11].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>. Combat related achievements are:
                        <span class="achievement">
                            <%= achievements[8].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[8].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[8].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>,
                        <span class="achievement">
                            <%= achievements[9].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[9].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[9].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>,
                        <span class="achievement">
                            <%= achievements[13].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[13].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[13].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>,
                        <span class="achievement">
                            <%= achievements[14].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[14].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[14].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>,
                        <span class="achievement">
                            <%= achievements[15].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[15].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[15].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span> and
                        <span class="achievement">
                            <%= achievements[24].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[24].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[24].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>. For
                        <span class="achievement">
                            <%= achievements[19].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[19].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[19].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span> you need to kill all enemy types multiple times and successfully complete all types of
                        missions, since Memories have a drop chance. Make sure to choose both options after successfully
                        finishing the Rescue synapses for
                        <span class="achievement">
                            <%= achievements[17].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[17].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[17].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span> and
                        <span class="achievement">
                            <%= achievements[18].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[18].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[18].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>.
                    </p>
                    <p class="indent">
                        While managing your daughters you will earn
                        <span class="achievement">
                            <%= achievements[10].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[10].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[10].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>,
                        <span class="achievement">
                            <%= achievements[12].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[12].icon %> alt="" />
