                        </span>.
                    </p>
                    <h2>Second Playthrough</h2>
                    <p class="indent">
                        What is left now is to finish the tutorial by defeating all enemies for
                        <span class="achievement">
                            <%= achievements[6].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[6].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[6].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span> and defeat all bosses in a single Recollection for
                        <span class="achievement">
                            <%= achievements[5].displayName %>
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src=<%= achievements[5].icon %> alt="" />
                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[5].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>.
                    </p>
                    <h3>Time Saving Resources</h3>
                    <p>
                        <a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2391126546" target="_blank">100%
                            Achievements</a> - Also includes a few general tips and guides for a couple achievements if
                        you
                        are having trouble, especially for the tutorial.<br>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rightColumn">
                <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dmdbza74n/image/upload/v1693154838/achievementroadmaps/othercideR_kxuokp.webp"
                    alt="" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section>
        <%- include('../partials/ach-list') %>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
    </footer>

    <script src="/main.js"></script>
</body>

</html>